### Top 10 Free API Keys for Creating Bots and Chatbots with AI

1. **OpenAI GPT-3.5 (Limited Free Access)**
   - **Description**: Provides advanced natural language understanding and generation.
   - **Features**: Text completion, conversation, translation.
   - **Limitations**: Limited usage on the free tier.
   - **Get It**: [OpenAI](https://beta.openai.com/signup/)

2. **Dialogflow**
   - **Description**: A natural language understanding platform for building conversational agents.
   - **Features**: Speech-to-text, text-to-speech, pre-built agents.
   - **Limitations**: Free tier with usage limits.
   - **Get It**: [Dialogflow](https://dialogflow.cloud.google.com/)

3. **Wit.ai**
   - **Description**: Adds natural language processing to applications with text and voice interaction.
   - **Features**: Intent recognition, entity extraction.
   - **Limitations**: Unlimited usage on the free tier.
   - **Get It**: [Wit.ai](https://wit.ai/)

4. **Microsoft Azure Cognitive Services (LUIS)**
   - **Description**: Provides natural language capabilities for apps, bots, and devices.
   - **Features**: Intent recognition, entity extraction, conversation logging.
   - **Limitations**: Free tier with limited usage.
   - **Get It**: [Microsoft Azure](https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/cognitive-services/language-understanding-intelligent-service/)

5. **IBM Watson Assistant**
   - **Description**: Conversational AI platform for building chatbots and virtual assistants.
   - **Features**: Pre-built content, multi-language support, analytics.
   - **Limitations**: Free tier with usage limits.
   - **Get It**: [IBM Cloud](https://www.ibm.com/cloud/watson-assistant)

6. **Rasa**
   - **Description**: An open-source framework for building conversational AI.
   - **Features**: Customizable NLU and dialogue management.
   - **Limitations**: Free and open-source, self-hosted.
   - **Get It**: [Rasa](https://rasa.com/)

7. **Botpress**
   - **Description**: An open-source conversational AI platform for building chatbots.
   - **Features**: Visual flow builder, modular architecture.
   - **Limitations**: Free and open-source, self-hosted.
   - **Get It**: [Botpress](https://botpress.com/)

8. **Snips NLU**
   - **Description**: An open-source natural language understanding library.
   - **Features**: Intent recognition, entity extraction, offline capabilities.
   - **Limitations**: Free and open-source, self-hosted.
   - **Get It**: [Snips](https://snips.gitbook.io/snips-nlu/)

9. **AIML (Artificial Intelligence Markup Language)**
   - **Description**: A language for creating natural language software agents.
   - **Features**: Rule-based chatbots, pattern-matching.
   - **Limitations**: Free and open-source, no hosting required.
   - **Get It**: [AIML](https://www.aiml.foundation/)

10. **ChatterBot**
    - **Description**: A Python library for creating conversational AI.
    - **Features**: Machine learning-based responses, easy integration.
    - **Limitations**: Free and open-source, Python-based.
    - **Get It**: [ChatterBot](https://chatterbot.readthedocs.io/)

---

These services offer a variety of options for building and deploying AI-powered chatbots, from cloud-based solutions to open-source frameworks.
